
PPA
===

This package is available here
https://launchpad.net/~bpaquet/+archive/crowd-apache2-modules

Changelog
===

Some improvments on http://confluence.atlassian.com/display/CROWD020/Integrating+Crowd+with+Apache

* Send Set-Cookie crowd.token_key header after first authentication
* Check if  Cookie crowd.token_key is present, and use it for authent. Call to check cookie to Crowd are cached.

News parameters
* CrowdCookieSet : add Set-Cookie header if needed, default value : false
* CrowdCookieName : default value : crowd.token_key
* CrowdCacheExpiryApp : cache expiry time for app cache, default value : 3600
